      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum elastic-plastic material model with isotropic hardening selected based on published titanium alloy characterization data; contact formulation validated against known analytical solutions.",
      "rationale": "Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) modeled with bilinear isotropic hardening; UHMWPE vertebral body blocks modeled as linear elastic. Model form selection is consistent with prior FDA-published pedicle screw FEA guidance and the literature. Frictionless augmented Lagrange contact was validated against Hertz contact benchmark. Required level 3 achieved."
