      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions match ASTM F1717 protocol including offset distance, load rate, and environmental conditions; multiple offset distances evaluated.",
      "rationale": "Testing was conducted per ASTM F1717 at a single 40 mm anterior offset distance and quasi-static load rate of 5 mm/min at ambient temperature. Only one offset distance was evaluated, which does not capture the full range of in vivo loading scenarios. This factor is below the required level 3; the gap is noted and accepted given that the 40 mm offset represents the standard worst-case condition per ASTM F1717. Achieved level 2."
